NAME

IPC::Filter - filter data through an external process

DESCRIPTION

The "filter" function provided by this module passes data through an
external command, thus providing filtering in non-pipeline situations.

INSTALLATION

	perl Build.PL
	./Build
	./Build test
	./Build install

